source confusion experienced by the WFM in crowded regions of\nthe sky like the Galactic Center and will in general increase the observatory\nscience capability of the mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2012 11:29:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
